clubSubtitle: Sponsor(s): Kelsey Ondish, Haley Care, Liz Paternoster
clubText: Student Government is the place to be to get involved in all things FHS. From organizing Homecoming week and Riley week to the Pasta Bowl, this club will get you locked in on all the major service and school spirit events that FHS has to offer. Check out this video and meet your Student Body Officers! https://youtu.be/DLIABkcfBw0
